Package: GLproxScape
Type: Package
Title: Spatial Deconvolution of dCas9-APEX2 Proximity Proteomics
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person(given = "Can",
                  family = "Ozcan",
                  role = c("aut", "cre"),
                  email = "s.canozcan89@gmail.com")
Description: Spatial deconvolution of dCas9-APEX2 proximity proteomics data
    into transcription factor and chromatin-regulator binding predictions.
    Models each guide's biotinylation footprint as a Gaussian labelling kernel
    around the cut site and recovers motif-anchored binding events via
    non-negative least squares against JASPAR position weight matrices.
    Includes coverage-aware deconvolution, optional PWM-score weighting, a
    zone-based path for sequence-specific-motif-less chromatin factors, and
    an optional ChIP-Atlas overlay for independent peak validation.
